cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper focuses on generating formal queries for question answering over knowledge bases, which involves natural language processing, information retrieval, and machine learning techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with knowledge bases, which falls under cs.DB (Databases) and involves machine learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
